   commit 29ace668ae756c7b8917c57abb440f6518844b0c — android17-release @ 2026-06-16.)

  Then:  repo sync   ->   bash <this-repo>/apply-aosp-patches.sh   (see README.md)
  All revisions below are pinned to exact SHAs for reproducibility.
-->
